t your dots set up on him how you like them.  Also, if the druid actually melees you, two can play that game.  With my epic I'm maxing around 44/hit currently.  Never know, you might get a lucky interrupt.</P><P>-Saleem<BR>Warlock of Xegony</P><P></font></td>
